beer.beer_description: Darker days means darker beers. Introducing 'All Night Long', A full bodied malt profile will dance across your mouth as you take a sip. Finishing crisp & clean due to the lager yeast we used. The perfect beer for those colder times, and certainly a brew you can enjoy all night loooong!

items.checkin_comment: Lionel Richie walks into a bar, orders a beer and the bartender asks: “Hey, why the long face?”  Coffee, toffee, black tea; malty, biscuity taste with a dryish, yeasty length and finish. Top class dark all night long. Lose yourself in wild romance.
